{"tid":1537072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（國際戰線）點樣令全世界不論左派定右派一齊撐香港","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T21:44:51.000Z","uid":287362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"00fe7bb8788ac4078b7f741cdb57e5dc2456e9fe","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:57:21.000Z","msg":"首先大家要知道 其實95%英國同美國人都唔妥共慘黨<br />\n但係唔知點解 香港民主嘅protest好似成為咗右派嘅宣傳嘅工具<br />\nso far 最撐港嘅議員都似係尼自保守黨, eg Tom Tugendhat; Bob Seely; marco rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheAtlIdeas/status/1168917366123708416?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheAtlIdeas%2Fstatus%2F1168917366123708416%3Fs%3D20&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=d1e62040\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheAtlIdeas%2Fstatus%2F1168917366123708416%3Fs%3D20&h=ab74fd19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TheAtlIdeas/status/1168917366123708416?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/IoWBobSeely/status/1168191003645399040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIoWBobSeely%2Fstatus%2F1168191003645399040&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=25b2dfbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIoWBobSeely%2Fstatus%2F1168191003645399040&h=e9af6e8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/IoWBobSeely/status/1168191003645399040</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1162420834994184204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1162420834994184204&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=a801f057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1162420834994184204&h=699465c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1162420834994184204</a><br />\n甚至係steve bannon （尼條友我最驚 佢講嘢不嬲冇句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_xDQs5M7lHw&amp;t=687s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_xDQs5M7lHw%26t%3D687s&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ae43e4d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_xDQs5M7lHw&amp;t=687s</a><br />\n（片４５分鐘長，但值得睇－有中文字幕<br />\n唔知點解佢愈撐港我愈驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n加拿大極右媒體rebel media 都為香港反共大做文章<br />\n搞到好似撐港=極右咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_E9U--8_9VU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_E9U--8_9VU&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=0ac5c7e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_E9U--8_9VU</a><br />\n<br />\n其實咁好危險 我哋絕對唔可以倫為不同政黨 政壇嘅一步棋<br />\n因為你睇到想pass撐港法案議員真係尼自唔同黨派 （which 喺E家brexit令英國完全五十五十咁分裂嘅狀態 － 簡稱係唯一一個議題係有共識咖）<br />\n請睇吓喱個tweet：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1168853798766465024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1168853798766465024&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=1f8dbb2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flukedepulford%2Fstatus%2F1168853798766465024&h=02bc6b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lukedepulford/status/1168853798766465024</a><br />\n睇到哩個撐港法案嘅endorsers真係尼自好多唔同黨派 － 請睇個note<br />\n有pro／anti brexit； 有pro／anti Scottish Independence；左中右有齊晒<br />\nC－conservative － 保守黨 （右）<br />\nL－labour－公黨（左）<br />\nLD － liberal democrats － 自由黨（中間）<br />\nSNP－Scottish independence party －蘇格蘭獨立黨（左）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以我地一定要重點發揚香港嘅protest係all about 人權，發治，民主 ；道德－ 普世價值<br />\n一定唔可以比人哋騎劫！！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2759306d9623cebf332fdf1a82e695457a3b843c","tid":1537072,"uid":33292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:59:57.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"f78f798cd9c570835d416de811eccce5b2e009ad","tid":1537072,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:00:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解散警隊 刻不容緩</span></strong></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TXKCPJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TXKCPJ.jpg&h=a6a9f88f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d49c3ebc7b4b6a3e6d4918f7a310a829362a54b5","tid":1537072,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈內容包括：</span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"15af135fedc1aa608a2d718320600c11b8d54d8b","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:06:05.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba824ae185c03ebacf35625be490d8a36ac289cf","tid":1537072,"uid":24944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:06:05.000Z","msg":"明明左報都好支持我哋"},{"pid":"6e6b05c703047ddeb8fdf7dbead36c0f5597fadf","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:07:37.000Z","msg":"人權 發治 民主 道德 普世價值<br />\n<br />\n唔好比敵人有位攝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9a573776cd87eba76c9ca0aed332dfa610edf1","tid":1537072,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:11:42.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">中國威脅論\n打壓外資 染紅企業\n清算航運龍頭大本營\n白色恐怖橫行\n貨幣操控 嚴重影響全球經濟\n反人道 暴力主義 阻礙救護\n反人權 軍事鎮壓\n誣陷扣留外國領事館職員\n公然宣佈國際聲明已成歷史\n人面識別系統全面入侵私隱\n智能燈柱RFID監察行動痕跡 5G WiFi隱患\n信用系統標籤分等 限制人身權利打壓異己\n施壓公共交通系統公司\n施壓司法機關系統\n掌控執法部門成管治機器\n新聞媒體自由封鎖 假新聞一言定音\n不容異見之聲 網絡圍牆封鎖屏蔽 \n宣揚一人執政黨國 造王英雄主義\n改造信仰 壓抑宗教自由\n中國人納粹主義浪潮入侵西方主義國家\n新疆教育營文化滅絕 非我族類 封村屠殺 毒針坐刑\n六四屠殺事件 歷史檔案依然封鎖\n維權人士牢獄之災 信用評等負分步步為艱 每年逃亡海外\n陳秋實律師片段、多位內地藝術家遭禁聲\n強制拘留 驗血 政治檢控 勞改\n人民日報種族歧視深膚色人種\n警隊以&lsquo;甲甴&rsquo;爭議厭惡性詞 代指運動人士\n過期催淚彈CS神經毒氣 大量存放使用 社區災難\n解僱 清算 追捕 人面拍攝 ID追蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"22b7768a4791a0aaa78a267b0d0cd2194b189d23","tid":1537072,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:12:11.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器 衝車廂 無調查 齋打人 純洩憤<br />\n情緒失控 行為失控 妄顧公眾安全 人身權利<br />\n濫暴 濫用私刑 酷刑凌辱 瀆職<br />\n施放過期神經毒氣 危害社區<br />\n公然妨礙新聞自由 <br />\n阻礙救援 違反國際人道法<br />\n封鎖現場多個小時 隔離救護員進入<br />\n截斷交通 封鎖去道<br />\n<br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span></span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n請求通過美國國會人權民主法案<br />\n<br />\n召喚攬炒巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66efdc315d343f33c52a3868eb7402adbdcc3d6d","tid":1537072,"uid":269119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:22:12.000Z","msg":"本店唔妥中國共產黨。<br />\n真正共產主義係快樂放題嘅和平自由民主。中共係獨裁，反人類，反承諾，反自由。<br />\n我係小紅帽。我係真紅。<br />\n蛋糕任食。願望共嘗。和平共享。<br />\n🍰🍰🍰🍰🍰"},{"pid":"a1a668e6cc2374e7e701f47b0e1915a336c748ca","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:22:36.000Z","msg":"個point係左派民主黨其實都支持緊香港<br />\n<br />\n由Nancy Polosi 佩洛西<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U7JLJ5yKK78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU7JLJ5yKK78&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=8c808034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U7JLJ5yKK78</a><br />\n到Chunk Schumer 舒默<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1167466099773976578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1167466099773976578&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=0ccc6c69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1167466099773976578&h=c8a7e2b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1167466099773976578</a><br />\n<br />\n根本美國 所有西方國家嘅人心底裡都支持香港<br />\n點解？因為我哋爭取緊嘅係普世價值 － 人權 發治 民主 道德"},{"pid":"fc6b46b3e93b4f21fcb96a55370d835e1b93ad1b","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a709894e31a4650ee7e4b65009c358b8ede7c2","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:02:19.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfc9e26323df55f7cec35a068b6bcd659c2f907","tid":1537072,"uid":287362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T21:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" cl